23rAt.png&h=43115143&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ffeb373474e430ee3880514529e056e437e471d","tid":1074232,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T09:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pHVXv2L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpHVXv2L.jpg&h=ccc64cff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zSeA19q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzSeA19q.png&h=66555d11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n名稱：蝦茶飯<br />\n材料：<br />\n米兩杯<br />\n冷綠茶 300 c.c<br />\n鹽一小匙<br />\n油豆腐皮一小片<br />\n乾燥蝦米 10 g<br />\n蔥末少許<br />\n步驟：<br />\nstep 1. 將 一小匙的鹽 和 300 c.c的綠茶 攪拌均勻<br />\nstep 2. 將 準備好的 油豆腐皮 切成細條狀<br />\nstep 3. 將 兩杯米 和 油豆腐皮 放到電鍋裡<br />\nstep 4. 將 乾燥蝦米 10 g 和 綠茶 也一併放進去<br />\nstep 5. 跟平常煮飯的量和方式都一樣<br />\nstep 6. 將飯盛出 撒上蔥末 即完成了"},{"pid":"60de14c78788e309f2090e4e83d3d59d8d36d39d","tid":1074232,"uid":139516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T09:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AeCbAvv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAeCbAvv.png&h=30f2c723&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b00df50b39c0aef62d1fa9301db9ea4910b111c6","tid":1074232,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T09:03:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FKdqEXp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFKdqEXp.jpg&h=bf3042c9&s={SIZE}\" /> 同快餐下午茶一樣"},{"pid":"70847db794ca8ab5f25f14332981d84bef984084","tid":1074232,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T09:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RTQTORR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRTQTORR.jpg&h=11479fac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CqEQQ5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCqEQQ5b.jpg&h=be4aceda&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}